ed="T" n="0881a06"/><persName key="A013740">釋幽玄</persName>，俗姓劉，<placeName key="PL000000000368">幽州</placeName>人也。夙懷出俗之願，<lb
ed="T" n="0881a07"/>年及弱冠，方遂前心，投<placeName key="PL000000003793">并州</placeName><persName key="A013743">賢禪師</persName>而了<lb
ed="T" n="0881a08"/>玄契。<date key="j20158562016209" notAfter-iso="+0808-02-03" notBefore-iso="+0807-02-15"><name>元和</name>二年</date>，振錫<placeName key="PL000000000197">江左</placeName>，至會稽<placeName key="PL000000013234">大雲寺</placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0881a09"/>見三學僧柅定食輪，資緣都闕。<persName key="A013740">玄</persName>言發響應，<lb
ed="T" n="0881a10"/>檀越供贍。未幾，移居<placeName key="PL000000013294">湖心龜山妙喜古寺</placeName>。<date key="j20183962018779" notAfter-iso="+0815-02-16" notBefore-iso="+0814-01-29">九<lb
ed="T" n="0881a11"/>年</date>，屬<placeName key="PL000000022160">平昌</placeName><persName key="A009184">孟簡</persName>鎮于<placeName key="PL000000013239">越</placeName>，枉駕問道，遂構成<lb
ed="T" n="0881a12"/>大院。<date key="j20194882019871" notAfter-iso="+0818-02-12" notBefore-iso="+0817-01-25">十二載</date>，復登<placeName key="PL000000028928">南嶽</placeName>，栖止絕頂。<date key="j20198722020226" notAfter-iso="+0819-02-02" notBefore-iso="+0818-02-13">十三年</date>，<lb
ed="T" n="0881a13"/><placeName key="PL000000018603">豫章</placeName>太守<persName key="A013741">商祐</persName>篤重其道，命住東明寺<!--找不到此地-->，即<persName key="A002828">東<lb
ed="T" n="0881a14"/>晉安帝</persName>世之所造，僧數繁湊。<date key="j20224182023128" notAfter-iso="+0827-01-13" notBefore-iso="+0825-02-02">寶曆中</date>，為奏改<lb
ed="T" n="0881a15"/>為世福<!--找不到此地-->，兼置戒壇，續勅改為度僧寺<!--找不到此地-->。其間<lb
ed="T" n="0881a16"/>形像，皆<persName key="A013740">玄</persName>之化導。<date key="j20231922023504" notAfter-iso="+0828-01-24" notBefore-iso="+0827-03-18">大和元年</date>，<persName key="A013742">沈<anchor xml:id="beg0881sgsz1"/>傅<anchor xml:id="end0881sgsz1"/></persName>中丞<ptr target="#n2043"/>又加<lb
ed="T" n="0881a17"/>信向。<persName key="A013740">玄</persName>於院南別造佛閣五層，功就，謂弟<lb
ed="T" n="0881a18"/>子曰：「福事無盡，生涯有期。物有闕然，後人<lb
ed="T" n="0881a19"/>庀具。<persName key="A013740">吾</persName>終後，可將屍漆布安閣下。」言訖而<lb
ed="T" n="0881a20"/>化，門人特旁立塔焉。</p>
